title: Foot
description: A human foot shown with five toes and may include part or all of the ankle. Shown on Apple platforms as the sole of a foot.
apple_vendor_description: Apple's foot emoji is a clean, simple representation rendered with smooth, rounded edges and subtle shading that gives it a soft, almost toy-like quality. The distinct shape, with a gentle curve and well-defined toes, appears polished and friendly. On Apple devices, this emoji can humorously signify walking, taking a step, or even a lighthearted gesture of putting one's foot down.
